ca.ualberta.cs.wrkify

Class TaskListAdapter<T extends Task>

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<TaskViewHolder>
      • ca.ualberta.cs.wrkify.TaskListAdapter<T>

  • public class TaskListAdapter<T extends Task>
extends android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<TaskViewHolder>
    Adapter for lists of Tasks or objects in that family. To be used as an adapter for RecyclerView whenever a potentially large list of Tasks is to be displayed Tasks are displayed as CardViews but can be easily changed to something else in TaskViewHolder.
    See Also:
    TaskViewHolder, SearchFragment
